Representation of what went wrong:

				-- ExceptionClass
				-- Message
				-- StackTrace

Flow Control:
				--Clean, Readable
				--Replaces if(bad) goto coding..
				
				
1) Checked Exceptions: All e: (!e instanceof RuntimeException)
Robust implementations should handle these cases: Repair the code!

2) Unchecked Throwable: Error
Usually catastrophic-unrecoverable: Ignore them in the coding context

3) Unchecked Throwable: RuntimeException
This is a bug! Debug it!